      <title>《基地三部曲》读后感</title>
      <link href="/posts/202208_49376.html"/>
      <url>/posts/202208_49376.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="douban-card-block">    <a class="douban-card" href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1258490">        <div class="douban-card-bgimg" style="background-image: url('https://images.weserv.nl/?url=https://img2.doubanio.com/view/subject/s/public/s1328663.jpg');">        </div>        <div class="douban-card-left">            <div class="douban-card-img" style="background-image: url('https://images.weserv.nl/?url=https://img2.doubanio.com/view/subject/s/public/s1328663.jpg');">            </div>            <div class="douban-card-status">见字如晤</div>        </div>        <div class="douban-card-right" style="line-height: 1.7;">            <div class="douban-card-item"><span>书名: </span><strong>基地</strong></div>            <div class="douban-card-item"><span>作者: </span><span>[美]艾萨克·阿西莫夫</span></div>            <div class="douban-card-item"><span>出版年份: </span><span>2005-1</span></div>            <div class="douban-card-item"><span>评分: </span><span>9.2</span></div>        </div>    </a></div><style>    .douban-card-block {    display: flex;    justify-content: center;    align-items: center;    width: 100%;    max-height: 400px;}.douban-card {    display: flex;    margin: 30px 10px;    padding: 15px;    border-radius: 15px;    position: relative;    justify-content: center;    align-items: center;    overflow: hidden;    color: antiquewhite;    text-decoration: none;}.douban-card:hover {    text-decoration: none;}.douban-card-bgimg {    position: absolute;    width: 115%;    height: 115%;    filter: blur(15px) brightness(0.6);    background-size: 100%;    background-position: center;    background-repeat: no-repeat;}.douban-card-img {    position: relative;    height: 130px;    width: 80px;    background-size: 100%;    background-position: center;    background-repeat: no-repeat;}.douban-card-left:hover .douban-card-img {    filter: blur(5px) brightness(0.6);    transform: perspective(800px) rotateX(180deg);}.douban-card-left .douban-card-img {    transition: all 500ms ease;}.douban-card-left {    position: relative;    display: flex;    flex-direction: column;    align-items: center;}.douban-card-left .douban-card-status {    height: 130px;    width: 80px;    text-align: center;    font-weight: bold;    position: absolute;    left: 0;    top: 30%;    transform: rotateX(180deg);    backface-visibility: hidden;    transition: all 500ms ease;}.douban-card-left:hover .douban-card-status {    transform: perspective(800px) rotateX(0deg);}.douban-card-right {    position: relative;    display: flex;    flex-direction: column;    margin-left: 12px;    font-size: 16px;    font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;    line-height: 1.3;    color: antiquewhite;}.douban-card-item {    margin-top: 4px;}</style><p>艾萨克·阿西莫夫，作为20世纪最著名的SF小说作家，《基地三部曲》早已在我的Todo list上挂了许久，最近才幸运地得以拜读。</p><p>要初读《基地》我只觉得惊叹于作者对未来的畅想，星际旅游、心理学家，以及作者对人类文明后续走向的细致把控。</p><p>到了第二部《基地与帝国》，科幻背景好像没那么重要了，整个故事只关乎不同阵营之间的政治博弈。</p><p>到第三部《第二基地》，则是唯心史观和唯物史观的碰撞，即强大的个人力量是否会影响历史的洪流走向。同时我又想到，基地与第二基地的存在，会不会只是心理学家做的一个巨大的社会实验呢？</p><p>总的来说，个人最喜欢第三部的情节设置和人物设置，充满了悬疑的味道。基地系列的后面几作之后有时间再补。</p><p>PS：每次看到书里对读书机的描写，总是很容易出戏，手机又何尝不是另类的读书机呢？其功能完全符合阿西莫夫的设想，但单从外形来看，两者又相差甚远，不得不说世界真奇妙。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
